1
00:01:40,110 --> 00:01:43,020
[Fangs of Fortune]

2
00:01:43,170 --> 00:01:45,990
[Episode 24]

3
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:36,760
Wen Zongyu, I'll kill you!

4
00:02:39,829 --> 00:02:40,750
If you kill me,

5
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:41,750
you'll die too.

6
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:44,780
What do you mean?

7
00:02:46,570 --> 00:02:47,950
Have you never felt

8
00:02:47,950 --> 00:02:50,310
the burning pain in your chest?

9
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:06,490
What did you do to me?

10
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:10,580
Whether it's used against a human or a demon,

11
00:03:11,220 --> 00:03:13,680
poison is always the most effective weapon.

12
00:03:14,150 --> 00:03:15,740
If you want to live,

13
00:03:16,329 --> 00:03:18,160
you have to listen to me.

14
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,560
I, Li Lun,

15
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:23,990
never take orders from anyone!

16
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:25,590
Really?

17
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,680
Imperial Physician Liu has checked on him.

18
00:03:58,079 --> 00:04:01,100
He said Zhuo has serious internal injuries

19
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:02,630
and his life is in danger.

20
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:05,360
He couldn't find the cause

21
00:04:05,830 --> 00:04:08,230
and can only keep him alive with medication

22
00:04:08,350 --> 00:04:10,000
and daily acupuncture.

23
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:13,540
Bingyi has many descendants,

24
00:04:14,190 --> 00:04:17,450
but only a few can be acknowledged by the Cloud Light Sword.

25
00:04:17,529 --> 00:04:19,730
Those who are acknowledged by the Sword

26
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,540
will empathize with it.

27
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,350
The Cloud Light Sword

28
00:04:25,930 --> 00:04:27,930
will then become his fate weapon.

29
00:04:29,850 --> 00:04:31,210
Fate weapon?

30
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,470
Having a fate weapon means that

31
00:04:36,420 --> 00:04:38,080
as long as the sword is intact,

32
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:39,650
its owner stays alive;

33
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:42,080
if the sword is destroyed,

34
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,300
its owner dies.

35
00:04:45,850 --> 00:04:46,550
So,

36
00:04:47,230 --> 00:04:49,050
that's the reason

37
00:04:49,710 --> 00:04:51,190
why Zhuo is in a coma.

38
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:57,250
I lost control of my malicious energy…

39
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:04,050
and caused the Cloud Light Sword to crack.

40
00:05:06,350 --> 00:05:08,560
Otherwise, Li Lun alone…

41
00:05:11,590 --> 00:05:14,650
wasn't powerful enough to break the Cloud Light Sword.

42
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:19,720
Zhuo tried his best to save me,

43
00:05:20,940 --> 00:05:21,780
but I…

44
00:05:24,550 --> 00:05:25,640
hurt him.

45
00:06:00,710 --> 00:06:02,150
If Jiu were here…

46
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,420
he'd definitely have a solution.

47
00:06:07,790 --> 00:06:08,810
Yes.

48
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:12,650
Jiu is the most famous young physician in Tiandu.

49
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:14,910
He cured a lot of people.

50
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:19,750
Ms. Pei.

51
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:21,740
Do you think

52
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:23,240
Jiu will

53
00:06:23,910 --> 00:06:25,830
return to the way he used to be?

54
00:06:31,010 --> 00:06:33,070
I'll definitely take him back

55
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:36,190
from Li Lun.

56
00:06:55,150 --> 00:06:55,870
Ah.

57
00:06:57,230 --> 00:06:57,870
How about

58
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,050
we ask Mr. Lu Wu about it?

59
00:07:00,350 --> 00:07:02,820
There are many rare herbs on Mount Kunlun.

60
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:03,910
Maybe

61
00:07:03,910 --> 00:07:05,110
Mr. Lu Wu has a way

62
00:07:05,110 --> 00:07:06,530
to cure Mr. Zhuo

63
00:07:06,710 --> 00:07:08,400
or wake Bai Jiu up.

64
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:13,120
Are you coming with me?

65
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:17,470
Yes.

66
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,060
Li Lun used his inner core

67
00:07:29,060 --> 00:07:30,890
to live in Bai Jiu.

68
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,060
It's much more powerful

69
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:34,080
than possession by spells.

70
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,820
