71
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,220
Is there

72
00:07:37,350 --> 00:07:39,020
no solution at all?

73
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,320
There is.

74
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:44,010
You need the help of Bingyi's descendants.

75
00:07:44,010 --> 00:07:45,030
They can use the Cloud Light Sword

76
00:07:45,030 --> 00:07:48,360
to separate the parasitic primordial spirit from the host.

77
00:07:48,470 --> 00:07:49,530
Cloud Light Sword?

78
00:07:50,590 --> 00:07:51,390
Mr. Zhuo?

79
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,690
But I heard

80
00:07:55,990 --> 00:07:58,320
the Cloud Light Sword has been destroyed.

81
00:08:00,090 --> 00:08:00,890
Mr. Lu Wu,

82
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:02,870
Mr. Zhuo

83
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:03,990
is in a coma now.

84
00:08:04,650 --> 00:08:05,750
Is there any way

85
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:06,900
to wake him up?

86
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:09,170
There is Gui Wood in the Wilderness.

87
00:08:09,170 --> 00:08:10,870
Eating it can restore his energy

88
00:08:10,870 --> 00:08:13,480
and slow down his deterioration.

89
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:15,230
Gui Wood?

90
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:17,650
Okay.

91
00:08:18,030 --> 00:08:19,040
I got it.

92
00:08:20,590 --> 00:08:21,380
Ms. Pei.

93
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,200
I'll send you back first.

94
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,290
I'll go with you.

95
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,360
