96
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:27,750
Gui Wood grows

97
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:29,820
in the crevices of black rocks along the seaside in the Wilderness.

98
00:08:29,820 --> 00:08:31,370
Sea scorpions are everywhere.

99
00:08:31,370 --> 00:08:33,370
There are also red-bellied snakes.

100
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,919
Since it's so dangerous,

101
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,320
I can't let you go alone.

102
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:39,309
You're still injured.

103
00:08:39,669 --> 00:08:40,780
Let me go.

104
00:08:40,809 --> 00:08:42,350
You're not familiar with the Wilderness,

105
00:08:42,350 --> 00:08:43,640
and there are demons everywhere.

106
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:44,520
I'll go.

107
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:46,190
I'll bring Gui Wood back.

108
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:48,280
Mr. Zhuo

109
00:08:48,350 --> 00:08:50,280
is the person Jiu admires the most.

110
00:08:50,950 --> 00:08:52,430
I must wake him up.

111
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:54,790
You should stay

112
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:56,170
to accompany Xiao.

113
00:08:57,170 --> 00:08:58,970
Goddess needs you more than I do.

114
00:09:10,230 --> 00:09:10,930
Sir.

115
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,400
You're back.

116
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,400
How do you feel?

117
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:30,960
Thank you

118
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,260
for your treatment.

119
00:09:33,310 --> 00:09:34,960
I'm right as rain now.

120
00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:36,940
Even better than I was

121
00:09:37,230 --> 00:09:38,230
before I got hurt.

122
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:45,190
Commander,

123
00:09:45,190 --> 00:09:46,190
according to the spy,

124
00:09:46,190 --> 00:09:49,520
Zhuo Yichen from the Demon Hunting Bureau is sick and dying.

125
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:54,890
Only Zhuo Yichen can kill Zhao Yuanzhou.

126
00:09:55,430 --> 00:09:57,130
He can't die!

127
00:10:04,950 --> 00:10:06,030
What's wrong?

128
00:10:14,770 --> 00:10:16,440
Wen Zongyu's poison.

129
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:18,870
Poison?

130
00:10:19,940 --> 00:10:21,330
This can wait.

131
00:10:22,310 --> 00:10:25,310
The most important thing now is the Cloud Light Sword.

132
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:30,040
It can remove my primordial spirit

133
00:10:30,990 --> 00:10:33,000
from Bai Jiu's body.

134
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:36,780
It's the only thing

135
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:39,150
I'm afraid of now.

136
00:10:39,950 --> 00:10:41,350
But the Cloud Light Sword

137
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,580
