138
00:10:46,770 --> 00:10:49,030
If we can't repair the Cloud Light Sword,

139
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,470
Zhuo will keep deteriorating

140
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:55,340
until he dies.

141
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:00,280
