142
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:05,000
The Cloud Light Sword could be destroyed,

143
00:11:05,850 --> 00:11:07,320
so it can be repaired.

144
00:11:10,950 --> 00:11:12,240
I'll go stop them.

145
00:11:12,870 --> 00:11:13,670
No need.

146
00:11:16,710 --> 00:11:18,410
