157
00:12:03,930 --> 00:12:05,760
Once awakened, the Cloud Light Sword

158
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,270
can shake the sun and moon

159
00:12:07,290 --> 00:12:08,860
and make the earth tremble.

160
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:11,890
As long as the one using it is strong enough,

161
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:15,460
the Cloud Light Sword will awaken on itself.

162
00:12:24,870 --> 00:12:27,930
Brother, you're so powerful but still can't wake it up.

163
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:30,830
I'm definitely hopeless.

164
00:12:42,010 --> 00:12:44,230
Yichen, have faith in yourself.

165
00:12:45,290 --> 00:12:46,640
After you grow up,

166
00:12:47,330 --> 00:12:49,790
you'll absolutely be more powerful than me.

167
00:12:53,070 --> 00:12:55,330
Then I'll try my best to catch up with you.

168
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,280
Okay.

169
00:13:00,670 --> 00:13:01,920
But later,

170
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,900
I'll go out with Father

171
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:06,060
