172
00:13:07,350 --> 00:13:08,520
When I come back,

173
00:13:08,540 --> 00:13:10,660
I'll teach you the technique just now,

174
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:11,510
okay?

175
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:13,750
Deal!

176
00:14:26,990 --> 00:14:28,120
Where is my brother?

177
00:14:32,770 --> 00:14:33,960
Say something.

178
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:38,490
Where is my brother?

179
00:15:27,590 --> 00:15:28,380
Brother.

180
00:15:30,390 --> 00:15:33,720
You promised to come back and teach me that sword technique.

181
