229
00:19:56,500 --> 00:20:00,950
It's the Bingyi Clan's secret heirloom that has been passed down through generations.

230
00:20:00,950 --> 00:20:02,150
Five-Colored Stone.

231
00:20:03,710 --> 00:20:05,920
The kind of stone that Nuwa used

232
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:08,380
to mend the sky back then?

233
00:20:09,040 --> 00:20:10,180
Yes.

234
00:20:11,470 --> 00:20:12,430
But why is it

235
00:20:12,430 --> 00:20:14,890
in the pool of the Demon Hunting Bureau?

236
00:20:14,910 --> 00:20:17,510
This mansion used to belong to the Zhuo family.

237
00:20:17,670 --> 00:20:20,790
The Zhuo family has kept the Five-Colored Stone for generations.

238
00:20:20,790 --> 00:20:22,580
It can mend the sky

239
00:20:23,150 --> 00:20:24,830
and repair everything.

240
00:20:25,430 --> 00:20:26,710
So I guess

241
00:20:28,700 --> 00:20:32,030
the Five-Colored Stone sensed the broken Cloud Light Sword

242
00:20:32,990 --> 00:20:34,710
and showed up itself.

243
00:20:35,290 --> 00:20:35,910
Great!

244
00:20:35,910 --> 00:20:36,470
But…

245
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:39,580
Zhuo can be saved.

246
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,330
Jiu?

247
00:21:20,420 --> 00:21:21,230
Li Lun.

248
00:21:22,990 --> 00:21:25,250
Do you have to destroy every hope we have?

249
00:21:25,790 --> 00:21:27,700
