274
00:24:14,910 --> 00:24:15,870
Ying Long,

275
00:24:16,300 --> 00:24:17,650
you don't mind dying,

276
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:20,660
but have you ever thought about my feelings?

277
00:24:23,510 --> 00:24:24,310
Bingyi?

278
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:46,730
Bingyi.

279
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:57,070
I see.

280
00:24:59,120 --> 00:25:02,310
Li Lun didn't come for the Five-Colored Stone.

281
00:25:02,550 --> 00:25:03,810
Then what does he want?

282
00:25:06,100 --> 00:25:07,640
He wants to turn Zhuo

283
00:25:10,870 --> 00:25:12,000
into a demon.

284
00:25:20,010 --> 00:25:20,870
Gui Wood!

285
00:25:20,900 --> 00:25:22,430
I've brought Gui Wood back.

286
00:25:32,770 --> 00:25:33,630
Mr. Zhuo.

287
00:25:34,410 --> 00:25:35,490
What's going on?

288
