00:41:55,590 --> 00:41:57,120
and Bai Jiu?

574
00:42:00,040 --> 00:42:01,930
Jiu is the youngest among us

575
00:42:03,310 --> 00:42:05,040
and doesn't know martial arts.

576
00:42:05,750 --> 00:42:07,110
He's very timid.

577
00:42:08,330 --> 00:42:09,910
When there was danger,

578
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:13,380
he always hid behind me and Zhuo.

579
00:42:15,460 --> 00:42:17,890
I wonder how he is now.

580
00:42:20,160 --> 00:42:21,580
Is he scared?

581
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,900
You treat Bai Jiu so well…

582
00:42:30,230 --> 00:42:31,870
like he's your own brother.

583
00:42:35,250 --> 00:42:37,200
I used to be weak and sick.

584
00:42:38,710 --> 00:42:40,510
You got used to taking care of me.

585
00:42:44,610 --> 00:42:46,250
Now that I'm a puppet,

586
00:42:48,310 --> 00:42:49,430
I don't feel pain

587
00:42:50,900 --> 00:42:52,150
or get hurt.

588
00:42:54,920 --> 00:42:56,770
I can protect you now.

589
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:00,630
But Bai Jiu is different.

590
00:43:02,520 --> 00:43:04,160
He really needs you.

591
00:43:06,000 --> 00:43:07,210
Is that why

592
00:43:08,600 --> 00:43:10,190
you care and worry

593
00:43:11,610 --> 00:43:12,820
so much about him?

594
00:43:20,720 --> 00:43:21,520
Yes.

595
00:43:28,270 --> 00:43:29,750
But Heng

596
00:43:29,770 --> 00:43:30,810
is Heng.

597
00:43:32,230 --> 00:43:33,900
You're never anyone else,

598
00:43:35,380 --> 00:43:37,360
and you'll never be.

599
00:43:40,860 --> 00:43:42,510
No one can replace you.

600
00:43:47,280 --> 00:43:50,010
With you fighting alongside me,

601
00:43:51,950 --> 00:43:54,260
I can protect others better.

602
00:44:03,630 --> 00:44:04,750
I'm happy

603
00:44:07,050 --> 00:44:09,210
that I'm no longer your burden.

604
00:44:09,460 --> 00:44:11,900
I've become your armor.

605
00:44:13,040 --> 00:44:13,840
But...

606
00:44:18,940 --> 00:44:20,090
But what?

607
00:44:26,930 --> 00:44:27,790
Nothing.

608
00:44:58,550 --> 00:44:59,190
Father.

609
00:44:59,880 --> 00:45:00,670
Cloud Light Sword.

610
00:45:00,670 --> 00:45:01,430
Zhuo.

611
00:45:01,800 --> 00:45:02,400
Cloud…

612
00:45:03,470 --> 00:45:04,490
Cloud Light Sword.

613
00:45:04,490 --> 00:45:05,410
Zhuo.

614
00:45:22,330 --> 00:45:23,460
Zhuo.

615
00:45:24,850 --> 00:45:26,110
Where are you going?

616
00:45:26,280 --> 00:45:27,110
Zhuo!
